      "fontSize": 16,
      "fontFamily": 1,
      "text": "Combat 战斗体模块\n\n• CombatBodyOrchestrator\n  编排激活/解除流程\n• CombatBodyRuntime\n  运行时聚合体\n• CombatBodyState\n  状态机 (Idle/Active/\n  Collapsing)\n• CombatBodySnapshot\n  快照恢复系统\n• EmergencyEscape\n  紧急脱离\n• HediffComp_TrionDrain\n  Trion 消耗组件",
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "Combat 战斗体模块\n\n• CombatBodyOrchestrator\n  编排激活/解除流程\n• CombatBodyRuntime\n  运行时聚合体\n• CombatBodyState\n  状态机 (Idle/Active/\n  Collapsing)\n• CombatBodySnapshot\n  快照恢复系统\n• EmergencyEscape\n  紧急脱离\n• HediffComp_TrionDrain\n  Trion 消耗组件",
      "lineHeight": 1.25,
      "baseline": 252
    },
