      "locked": false,
      "fontSize": 16,
      "fontFamily": 1,
      "text": "Trigger 触发体/芯片模块 (最复杂)\n\n• CompTriggerBody (13个分部类)\n  槽位管理 | 激活逻辑 | Verb系统 | 切换状态机\n• ChipSlot 芯片槽位数据\n• IChipEffect 芯片效果接口\n  - VerbChipEffect (注入Verb)\n  - HediffChipEffect (添加Hediff)\n  - PassiveChipEffect (被动效果)\n• ShotPipeline 射击管线\n  Aim阶段 → Fire阶段 (模块化)\n• DualWeapon 双武器系统\n  Verb_BDPRangedBase | Verb_BDPDual | Verb_BDPCombo\n• Shield 护盾系统\n  方向判定 | 成功率 | Trion消耗",
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "Trigger 触发体/芯片模块 (最复杂)\n\n• CompTriggerBody (13个分部类)\n  槽位管理 | 激活逻辑 | Verb系统 | 切换状态机\n• ChipSlot 芯片槽位数据\n• IChipEffect 芯片效果接口\n  - VerbChipEffect (注入Verb)\n  - HediffChipEffect (添加Hediff)\n  - PassiveChipEffect (被动效果)\n• ShotPipeline 射击管线\n  Aim阶段 → Fire阶段 (模块化)\n• DualWeapon 双武器系统\n  Verb_BDPRangedBase | Verb_BDPDual | Verb_BDPCombo\n• Shield 护盾系统\n  方向判定 | 成功率 | Trion消耗",
      "lineHeight": 1.25,
      "baseline": 252
    },
