      "text": "Projectiles 投射物\n\n• Bullet_BDP\n  v5管线架构\n• 8阶段管线:\n  - PostLaunchInit\n  - LifecycleCheck\n  - FlightIntent\n  - PositionModifier\n  - VisualObserve\n  - ArrivalPolicy\n  - HitResolve\n  - Impact\n• 模块工厂\n  配置→模块映射\n• GuidedModule\n  引导飞行",
